859
00:29:04,719 --> 00:29:06,119
"Bu ke shi yi"?

860
00:29:06,119 --> 00:29:07,079
"Bu ke shi yi"?

861
00:29:07,079 --> 00:29:08,439
"Bu Ke Si Yi".
[*Unbelievable]

862
00:29:08,439 --> 00:29:09,439
Unbelievable.

863
00:29:12,479 --> 00:29:15,079
