867
00:29:22,599 --> 00:29:23,319
Born with curly hair.

868
00:29:23,319 --> 00:29:23,839
Guess a place name.

869
00:29:24,359 --> 00:29:26,000
A place in Southeast Asia.

870
00:29:28,280 --> 00:29:29,280
Southeast Asia.

871
00:29:31,079 --> 00:29:32,800
Born with curly hair.

872
00:29:33,959 --> 00:29:35,280
Is this Chinese-English too?

873
00:29:35,719 --> 00:29:36,160
No.

874
00:29:36,160 --> 00:29:37,359
