881
00:29:50,719 --> 00:29:51,719
Because it doesn't need curling.

882
00:29:51,719 --> 00:29:53,239
No electricity.
[*Homophonic to Myanmar in Chinese]

883
00:29:53,239 --> 00:29:53,839
Wow...

884
00:29:53,839 --> 00:29:56,079
(Need a quick "save")
What does this have to do with curls?

885
00:29:56,520 --> 00:29:57,599
Too farfetched.

886
00:29:58,920 --> 00:29:59,959
Fine, you're good-looking,

887
00:29:59,959 --> 00:30:02,079
so you're right.

888
00:30:02,319 --> 00:30:03,160
You're right.

889
