The answer...

892
00:30:10,000 --> 00:30:11,000
The answer to your question

893
00:30:11,000 --> 00:30:12,520
just needs one word to be related.

894
00:30:16,719 --> 00:30:18,359
Did you play butterfly catching before?

895
00:30:20,079 --> 00:30:20,880
No.

896
00:30:21,040 --> 00:30:21,640
No.

897
00:30:21,640 --> 00:30:22,239
What?

898
00:30:22,239 --> 00:30:23,839
Okay, butterfly catching.

899
00:30:23,839 --> 00:30:25,199
