900
00:30:25,199 --> 00:30:27,439
Catch butterflies.

901
00:30:27,439 --> 00:30:29,119
Catch butterflies.

902
00:30:29,119 --> 00:30:30,319
How many did I catch?

903
00:30:30,848 --> 00:30:33,289
(Allow me to do some quick calculations)

904
00:30:33,719 --> 00:30:34,920
None.

905
00:30:34,920 --> 00:30:35,560
Wrong.

906
00:30:35,560 --> 00:30:36,959
You need to find the pattern.

907
00:30:37,239 --> 00:30:38,359
I caught four.

908
00:30:38,479 --> 00:30:39,319
Again.

909
00:30:39,400 --> 00:30:40,599
Count carefully.

910
00:30:41,319 --> 00:30:42,239
You need to count.

911
00:30:42,239 --> 00:30:44,319
Catch butterflies.

912
00:30:44,479 --> 00:30:45,599
Catch butterflies.

913
00:30:45,599 --> 00:30:46,680
How many did I catch?

914
