922
00:31:04,640 --> 00:31:05,719
Nine-square grid, right?

923
00:31:05,719 --> 00:31:07,000
I get it.

924
00:31:07,457 --> 00:31:07,959
(I've got it)

925
00:31:07,959 --> 00:31:09,119
What else?

926
00:31:09,520 --> 00:31:10,520
Xuan is still confused.

927
